Title: Trouble In The Pines
Description:
There's been a primalist attack in the Shikaar Highlands.

If you have information or think you can help, head over to Pinewood Post and look for Olekk. Tell him I sent you. <Tirren chuckles.> I sure hope the dusty hoofer remembers me.

Keep to the roads, $p. The plains are not as peaceful since all this change arrived.
ObjectivesText: Speak to Sentinel Olekk at Pinewood Post in the Ohn'ahran Plains.
RewardText:
Tirren? He's still hoofing around, is he?

Thank you for coming. We can use all the help we can get.
